(zolmH 11 nouhembor 1888, mokka; mornnH 23 februvari 1958, dehli). Bhartacho ek mukhel rajki fuddari. Hachem mull namv mohiud'din ohmod oxem asun obulokolam' (vachspoti) hi tachi podvi. Tachea fuddem azhad (svotontr) hem ttopnnonamv to laitalo. Tacho zolm' eka vidvan ghoranneant zalo. Tachem lhanponn mokkek gelem. Orbi ani farsi to bapaikoddosun xiklo. Bapaivangodda 1890 to to kolokteak ailo. Paromparik muslomani xikxonnopdhdotipromann tannem farsi, urdu, orbi, hea bhasanchem xikop poilim korun torkoxastr,islam' dhorm', totvoginean ani gonnit hancho obheas kelo. Fuddem sor soiyod ohmodokhan hachea lekhancho porinnam' zaun tannem inglix bhaxecho obheas svotontroponnan suru kelo. Lhan pirayecher 1902 posun tannem nemalleamni lekh boroupak survat keli. 1905 to lokhnouchea ‘ on-nodva ’ hea potracho to sompadok zalo. Tea uprant don vorsamni to omritosor gelo ani thoinchea ‘ vokil ’ hea potracho sompadok zalo. 1908 to ijipt, orobstan, turkostan, frams hea dexank tannem bhett dili. Thoinchea krantiviranchea somprkak lagun tachim rajki-i motam bodlopak laglim ani kolokt'ta porot yetkoch hindi muslomanamni svatontry zhuzant vantto gheucho oxem mot tannem manddlem. Lok zagritayekhatir 1912 to kolokt'ta hanga tannem svotachem ‘ ol-hilal hem urdu satollem suru kelem. Urdu bhaxent hache adim itlea unchelea pamvddeachem nemallem yeunk naxil'lem. Nemalleamni, khobreptramni ‘ azhad ’ hea ttoponn namvan to boroitalo. Vrit'toptrachem sompadon korta astona to french xiklo.

‘ ol-hilal ’ potrant kel'le khor rajki ttikek lagun brittix sorkaran tachekoddosun 10,000 rupeancho zamin maglo. Tannem to dilona mhunn tem vrit'toptr bond poddlem. 1915 to tannem ‘ ol-boladh ’ hem dusrem disallem suru kelem. Taka lagun azhad haka khubxa prantamni vochpak sorkaran bondi ghali. Fuddem taka sanchi hanga sthanobdhd kelo. Tache ottkek lagun musloman khubll'lle. 1920 to to bondkhonnintlean suttlo. Oshokarachea cholloullint vantto ghetlo mhunn porot 1921 to taka ottok zali. Punn eka vorsa uprant taka mukt kelo. 1923 to dil'lik khaxelea kangres odhivexonacho to odhyokx zalo. 1930 to taka porthun bondkhonnint ghalo. 1930-31 hea don vorsant kaim musloman lok soteagrohant samil zale, hachem sogllem xrey azhadak fauta.

1939 te 1946 meren to kangresocho odhyokx axil'lo. 1942 to bharot chhoddochea soteagrohavellar taka porot bondkhonnint vochchem poddlem. 1945 to her fuddareamvangodda tachi suttka zali. 1942 chi krips yeuzonn, 1945 chi veuhelochi simla porixod ani 1946 to brittix montreanchem xixttomonddoll hea prosongantlea sogllea vattaghattint kangresourovim odhyokx hea natean tannench fuddakar ghetlo. 1947 to svotontrotai mell'llea uprant to kendri-i montrimonddollant ailo ani xikxonnomontri mhunn okheromeren thoinch urlo. Ek khampo uloupi mhunn tannem namna melloili. Tachem inglix, urdu, french, orbi ani farsi bhaxancher probhutv axl'lem. Tannem taitea nemalleantlean, khobreptrantolean sfutt boroup kelem. Urdu bhaxentolo to ek vhoddlea tankicho sahityokar zaun asa. Tachim kaim namnechim urdu pustokam oxim- ‘ tojkera ’, ‘ gubbare-khatir ’, ‘ koule-foisol ’, ‘ dastane korbola ’, ‘ mozamine ol hilal ’, ‘ mozamine azad ’, ‘ khutbate azad ’, ‘ imsaniyot mout ke dorvaje por ’. Tannem boroil'lo ‘ torzumanul koran ’ ho kurannocho urdu onnkar khub lokpriy zalo. ‘ inddia vins friddom' ’ (1959) hem tachem atmochoritr mornnauporant ujvaddak ailem. Hea atmochoritrantolo 30 panancho vantto rajki nodren vadgrost thartolo hea hixoban adinch koddek kaddun douril'lo. He sombondi prokaxok ani prokaxonache hokk axil'lea moulana azhad kolamachea varsodaram'modim vad zalo. Tachim uloupam-i pustokorupan halinch ujvaddak aileant.

